federal appeals court refused
to reinstate his travel ban.

29:27.966 --> 29:32.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Tomorrow, Attorney General Jeff
Sessions will testify in front
of the Senate Intelligence

29:34.166 --> 29:37.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Committee's open hearing
on Russia, all this
amid growing criticism
some fellow Republicans

29:38.833 --> 29:40.933 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
over the weekend.

29:40.933 --> 29:44.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
For more on how all of this
is affecting the White House,
we turn to Christopher Ruddy.

29:44.133 --> 29:49.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He's the CEO of the
conservative Newsmax Media and
a friend of President Trump.

29:50.566 --> 29:52.200 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Christopher Ruddy, thank
you for joining us again.

29:52.200 --> 29:54.800 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
So, we know you have
been talking to folks
inside the White House.

29:54.800 --> 29:59.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Last week had to have been one
of the most difficult weeks
for this young presidency,

30:01.233 --> 30:03.333 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
with the Comey testimony,
other matters out there.

30:03.333 --> 30:05.366 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
How is the president,
how are his team doing?

30:05.366 --> 30:08.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CHRISTOPHER RUDDY, CEO, Newsmax:
Well, I think they came out
of last week pretty good.

30:08.600 --> 30:13.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I spoke to the president late
last week, and I think he was
pretty optimistic about things

30:15.066 --> 30:18.466 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
and happy that things -- I
wouldn't say overly happy.

30:18.466 --> 30:23.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But I also think that he
generally felt that he had won a
victory, that Director Comey's

30:24.900 --> 30:28.866 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
