that there was no obstruction.

30:28.866 --> 30:33.166 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The director doesn't want to
describe what the president
said to him as obstruction.

30:33.166 --> 30:36.200 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
There is no evidence
of collusion.

30:36.200 --> 30:41.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We have a special prosecutor,
Judy, that has been appointed
here where there was never

30:42.433 --> 30:44.800 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
an allegation of a crime
or evidence of a crime.

30:44.800 --> 30:49.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
This is a very highly situation
-- highly unusual situation,
but it's also, I think,

30:51.200 --> 30:53.200 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
politically driven.

30:53.200 --> 30:57.433 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I think that that's getting
the president and a lot of
his top aides concerned that

30:59.500 --> 31:03.266 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
there is an effort here
to undermine his agenda
in Washington by people
that want to focus

31:04.000 --> 31:06.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
on these investigations.

31:06.000 --> 31:09.433 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Well, you're
saying it may be politically
motivated, but even Republicans

31:11.266 --> 31:15.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
on the Senate Intelligence
Committee said of former
Director Comey's testimony that

31:15.300 --> 31:19.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
