Office, in the White House, and
that whether his conversations

35:15.866 --> 35:18.733 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
with Director Comey
could have been recorded.

35:18.733 --> 35:21.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Do you know whether there
is a recording system
in the White House?

35:21.233 --> 35:22.900 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
CHRISTOPHER RUDDY: I hope not.

35:22.900 --> 35:25.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
I don't want any
of my conversations
with him out there.

35:25.000 --> 35:26.466 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
I don't know.

35:26.466 --> 35:27.633 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I can't remember half
the things I said to him.

35:27.633 --> 35:29.666 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
But...

35:29.666 --> 35:32.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Why do you think
he has not - - why do you think
he has declined to clarify

35:32.966 --> 35:34.200 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
that?

35:34.200 --> 35:36.266 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
CHRISTOPHER RUDDY:
Well, I don't know.

35:36.266 --> 35:39.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I think he was -- the way I
interpreted the president's
remark was that, if there were

35:39.733 --> 35:43.733 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
tapes, that they would vindicate
the president and not Comey.

35:43.733 --> 35:48.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I -- maybe he loves having that
out as a mystery out there, but
I'm not interpreting that that

35:50.333 --> 35:52.366 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
there's actual physical tapes.

35:52.366 --> 35:56.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: All right,
Chris Ruddy with Newsmax,
thank you very much.

35:57.566 --> 35:58.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
We appreciate it.

35:58.833 --> 36:00.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
CHRISTOPHER RUDDY: Great
to be on with you, Judy.

36:00.900 --> 36:04.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And to continue
our politics conversation,
