Inside Elections.

36:10.800 --> 36:11.600 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Thank you both.

36:11.600 --> 36:13.733 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
It's good to have you.

36:13.733 --> 36:16.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, Tam, you just heard Chris
Ruddy, who does talk to people
in the White House -- he said

36:16.800 --> 36:21.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
