we were aware of?

36:25.966 --> 36:29.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
TAMARA KEITH, National Public
Radio: Certainly, there has
been stuff around on Twitter of

36:29.933 --> 36:33.000 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
