questions about Mueller.

36:33.000 --> 36:38.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But the way that Ruddy just
couched that, he made it
clear that -- and maybe he was

36:39.866 --> 36:41.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
