with the president, possibly to
take the job of FBI director,

36:59.600 --> 37:03.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
which is a job he
had held before.

37:03.000 --> 37:07.200 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
NPR and Carrie Johnson,
my colleague at NPR,
had been reporting that
Mueller had met with

37:07.200 --> 37:10.566 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Justice Department officials
and also White House officials.

37:10.566 --> 37:14.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But the idea that he also met
with the president himself
is new, to me at least.

37:14.933 --> 37:19.933 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Stu
Rothenberg, this is --
these are -- the story
just keep bubbling up about

37:22.633 --> 37:27.133 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
Mr. Mueller, Mr. Comey,
the president, the
Russia investigation.

37:27.133 --> 37:31.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
This is a White House that,
this week, is trying to get
-- clearly get away from this.

37:31.466 --> 37:32.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
STUART ROTHENBERG,
Inside Elections: Right.

37:32.966 --> 37:37.033 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: They have labeled
