37:37.033 --> 37:42.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
What -- can they have -- can
they make any progress in
changing direction when you have

37:43.500 --> 37:44.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
this kind of
conversation going on?

37:44.500 --> 37:46.566 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
STUART ROTHENBERG: Right.

37:46.566 --> 37:48.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I think it's a great idea
