floor and any step he takes,
he's going to crunch something.

38:25.466 --> 38:27.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, I think it would be a
wonderful idea for the White
House to change the subject, but

38:27.600 --> 38:29.333 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
you can see what happened
in the last 24 hours.

38:29.333 --> 38:30.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: But, Tam,
they're still trying.

38:30.966 --> 38:32.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Last week, it was
infrastructure week.

38:32.333 --> 38:33.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
TAMARA KEITH: And
that was not...

38:33.333 --> 38:34.333 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And Mr. Comey.

38:34.333 --> 38:35.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
TAMARA KEITH: Yes.

38:35.333 --> 38:36.833 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

38:36.833 --> 38:38.100 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
TAMARA KEITH: And Mr. Comey
week is actually what it was.

38:38.100 --> 38:40.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And so the president
is flying tomorrow.

38:40.633 --> 38:44.533 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
He's going to Waukesha,
Wisconsin, to tour a
technical college and talk
about apprenticeships.

38:46.533 --> 38:51.366 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
On a slow news day, any other
president, that might sort of
be a headline, but it certainly

38:52.633 --> 38:55.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
wouldn't be a
front-page headline.

38:55.033 --> 39:00.100 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
If you're trying to distract
some very big headlines, going
to a technical college isn't

39:00.833 --> 39:01.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
necessarily the answer.

39:01.633 --> 39:03.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Here's the other thing.

39:03.633 --> 39:06.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We have been trying to press
the White House to find out
what policy change the president

39:06.600 --> 39:11.600 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
actually envisions or
they say that they want
more private-to-private
partnerships, to do

39:12.333 --> 39:13.800 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
more apprenticeships.

39:13.800 --> 39:15.300 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Around this
work force development, right.

39:15.300 --> 39:17.400 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
TAMARA KEITH: Exactly, around
this work force development.

39:17.400 --> 39:19.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But then they're saying, well,
you will have to wait until
Wednesday to find out exactly

39:19.800 --> 39:21.833 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
what we're talking about.

39:21.833 --> 39:25.666 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And that's a long time to
wait and it's a long time to
expect people to pay attention

39:25.666 --> 39:29.033 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
to something that is not related
to the biggest news of the day.

39:29.033 --> 39:30.366 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
STUART ROTHENBERG:
Two other points.

39:30.366 --> 39:33.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
One is, are there tapes?

39:33.333 --> 39:36.366 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
