considering the firing
of the special counsel.

39:43.300 --> 39:46.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Isn't that the next
week's discussion now?

39:46.233 --> 39:48.366 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
So, it's hard for me
to believe that...

39:48.366 --> 39:50.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Well, and we
couldn't tell - - as Tamara
was saying, we couldn't tell

39:50.633 --> 39:55.433 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
