lawyers is saying, but the fact

39:55.433 --> 39:56.933 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
that he said it has...

39:56.933 --> 39:58.133 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
STUART ROTHENBERG: And the way
he said it, yes, absolutely.

39:58.133 --> 39:59.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: .. has
to make us wonder.

39:59.500 --> 40:01.566 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
TAMARA KEITH: Stunning.

40:01.566 --> 40:04.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Well, as you
mentioned, Stu, you have got
the travel ban decision today

40:04.800 --> 40:06.066 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
