40:06.066 --> 40:09.133 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
There doesn't seem
to be good news.

40:09.133 --> 40:14.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I mean, health care reform
seems to be, at least for the
time being, slogged, stopped

40:15.366 --> 40:16.566 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
up.

40:16.566 --> 40:17.500 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Stopped up, is that
the word in the Senate?

40:17.500 --> 40:18.733 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
