tax reform plan.

40:23.633 --> 40:27.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
Are we just going to
watch the news develop
every week like this?

40:27.033 --> 40:28.266 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
And...

40:28.266 --> 40:29.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
STUART ROTHENBERG:
Yes, I think so.

40:29.966 --> 40:31.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
So, there is a problem
for the White House
on a number of levels.

40:31.633 --> 40:33.733 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
The president wants to
change the narrative.

40:33.733 --> 40:35.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
He also wants to
accomplish things.

40:35.166 --> 40:36.166 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
He hasn't yet.

40:36.166 --> 40:38.166 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Maybe he will.

40:38.166 --> 40:42.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But one of the things I believed
for many weeks and months is
that he has to worry about

40:43.433 --> 40:45.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
