just -- they don't want that.

41:03.566 --> 41:05.666 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
They want things to
return to normal.

41:05.666 --> 41:09.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And Donald Trump's -- the
whole premise of Donald
Trump is upsetting normal.

41:09.466 --> 41:14.266 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Well, you can only do that if
you accomplish certain things
and people start to feel better

41:14.266 --> 41:16.200 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
about themselves
and the country.

41:16.200 --> 41:18.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: How much do
