43:58.000 --> 44:01.100 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Next: screening
for cervical cancer in places
where the disease rarely

44:03.700 --> 44:07.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
gets priority, amid
other pressing problems.

44:07.333 --> 44:12.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Special correspondent Fred de
Sam Lazaro has a report on one
effort to prevent a disease

44:14.333 --> 44:17.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
that afflicts about 500,000
women across the world every
year, but has the most deadly

44:18.900 --> 44:20.933 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
outcomes in India.

44:20.933 --> 44:24.266 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
It's part of his ongoing
series Agents for Change.

44:24.266 --> 44:29.266 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: In a village
just outside Lucknow, India,
recently, there was a rare

44:30.666 --> 44:34.566 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
opportunity for many women
like 35-year-old Kiran Rawat.

44:34.566 --> 44:38.866 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
For the first time in her
life, she saw a doctor.

44:38.866 --> 44:42.333 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Her timing couldn't be better.

44:42.333 --> 44:47.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WOMAN (through translator):
There are some white spots
that I found when I applied the

44:47.200 --> 44:48.200 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
medicine.

44:48.200 --> 44:49.466 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
It's nothing to be afraid of.

44:49.466 --> 44:51.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: The
white spots are lesions.

44:51.433 --> 44:56.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
If left untreated, they can
lead to cervical cancer in
women usually between 30 and 60

44:56.633 --> 44:58.066 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
years old.

44:58.066 --> 45:00.433 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
It is preventable and
treatable if detected early.

45:00.433 --> 45:05.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Yet, more than half the cases
worldwide are fatal, the vast
majority of them in developing

45:06.900 --> 45:08.933 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
countries.

45:08.933 --> 45:12.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
In India, cervical cancer claims
almost 70,000 lives a year,
more than anywhere else in the

45:14.066 --> 45:16.133 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
world.

45:16.133 --> 45:20.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
That's because, for millions
of women here, seeing a doctor
is the last resort, an often

45:22.200 --> 45:24.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
unaffordable luxury.

45:24.433 --> 45:29.433 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But a pilot program run by the
global nonprofit Population
Services International, or PSI,

45:30.166 --> 45:32.266 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
aimed to change that.

45:32.266 --> 45:37.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The organization set up medical
screening camps in Uttar
Pradesh, India's most populous

45:37.200 --> 45:40.200 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
and one of its most
impoverished state.

45:40.200 --> 45:42.466 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Sixty women came to this one.

45:42.466 --> 45:45.233 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Four tested positive for
the pre-cancerous lesions

45:45.233 --> 45:47.766 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

45:47.766 --> 45:50.966 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
UMA SINGH, India: Pick
up a nice ball of cotton,
dip it in freshly made
acetic acid solution.

45:50.966 --> 45:55.966 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO:
In rich countries, Pap
smears and follow-up
treatment are the standard,

45:57.266 --> 45:59.600 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
but that's neither affordable
nor practical here.

45:59.600 --> 46:04.366 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Instead, obstetrics professor
Uma Singh demonstrated
to students a low-tech,
low-cost alternative

46:05.900 --> 46:09.600 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
being used in the pilot,
a simple swab of the
cervix with vinegar.

46:09.600 --> 46:11.600 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

46:11.600 --> 46:15.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
UMA SINGH: So, after one minute,
what you do is, do -- do the
inspection with good light.

46:17.666 --> 46:21.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, if you see a white area,
you treat it by a procedure
which is called cryotherapy.

46:22.933 --> 46:24.666 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO:
Literally freezing it off.

46:24.666 --> 46:26.166 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

46:26.166 --> 46:27.566 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
UMA SINGH: Yes, that's the
right word, freezing it off.

46:27.566 --> 46:29.533 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: The
lesions are a virus called HPV.

46:29.533 --> 46:34.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The patient can't see or
feel it, and the immune
system usually fights it off.

46:35.933 --> 46:39.133 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
However, about one in every
100 infections turns cancerous.

46:39.133 --> 46:43.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Vaccines are available
and have proven effective
in preventing HPV.

46:43.600 --> 46:46.733 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
But the cost puts them out of
reach of most Indian women.

46:46.733 --> 46:48.233 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

46:48.233 --> 46:49.133 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
SMITHA SINGH, India (through
translator): Don't be afraid.

46:49.133 --> 46:50.300 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
I will remove them.

46:50.300 --> 46:52.366 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
It's a very simple
thing, just 10 minutes.

46:52.366 --> 46:56.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: The
approach here is to remove
any lesions right away.

46:56.133 --> 47:01.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
There's no time or resources
to monitor or biopsy, no
assurance the women will return

47:01.866 --> 47:04.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
for follow-up treatment.

47:04.000 --> 47:08.366 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It is likely that in many,
if not most cases, you are
over-treating the patient.

47:08.833 --> 47:10.966 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

47:10.966 --> 47:13.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
UMA SINGH: Yes, it may be a
little bit of over-treating,
but it has been seen that it

47:13.866 --> 47:18.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
doesn't produce any substantial
harm to the woman in relation
to producing any long-term

47:20.300 --> 47:22.266 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
effects on the cervix.

47:22.266 --> 47:25.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: But, often,
women who test positive are
scared off by the prospect

47:25.966 --> 47:26.966 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
of cryotherapy.

47:26.966 --> 47:28.466 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

47:28.466 --> 47:30.733 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
SMITHA SINGH: They feel a
big treatment will be done.

47:30.733 --> 47:33.400 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And at times, they do not
give consent for the cryo.

47:33.400 --> 47:38.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: PSI
canvasser Pinky Rawat says that
happens for a simple reason.

47:40.900 --> 47:42.366 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PINKY RAWAT, Population
Services International
(through translator):
They hear the word cancer

47:42.366 --> 47:45.133 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
and they say, if I do have
cancer, what can I do?

47:45.133 --> 47:47.600 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
They get very scared
when they hear cancer.

47:47.600 --> 47:52.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: But even
as there's fear of cancer,
getting women to the screening

47:53.433 --> 47:56.766 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
was a tough sell.

47:56.766 --> 48:01.466 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
These women complained
that they need help for
far more mundane health
care issues, which

48:01.466 --> 48:02.966 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
no one provides.

48:02.966 --> 48:06.233 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
WOMAN (through translator):
My legs hurt all the time.

48:06.233 --> 48:08.266 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Give me something for my gout.

48:08.266 --> 48:11.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: Many women
labor in the field and in
households struggling to get

48:11.633 --> 48:13.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
by, and they neglect
their own health.

48:13.833 --> 48:16.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
SONI GUPTA, Population
Services International
(through translator):
It's affected my own

48:16.966 --> 48:18.233 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
family.

48:18.233 --> 48:20.200 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
It's been three months
since my mother died.

48:20.200 --> 48:23.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: PSI worker
Soni Gupta says early screening
and treatment might have

48:23.733 --> 48:26.566 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
saved her mother, who
died from cervical cancer.

48:26.566 --> 48:29.033 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
SONI GUPTA (through
translator): I feel terrible.

48:29.033 --> 48:32.266 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Even though I work in this field
for women, my own mother died.

48:32.266 --> 48:36.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: Of the
four women who tested positive
for the pre-cancerous lesions,

48:36.900 --> 48:41.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the social workers the next
morning were able to find just
one willing to go in and get

48:42.700 --> 48:43.800 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
treated.

48:43.800 --> 48:45.100 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
WOMAN (through
translator): I'm afraid.

48:45.100 --> 48:47.133 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
I have four children.

48:47.133 --> 48:50.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: It was
Kiran Rawat who needed a lot
of coaxing and reassurance by

48:50.600 --> 48:52.300 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
a PSI outreach worker.

48:52.300 --> 48:55.266 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
WOMAN (through translator):
There's nothing to worry about.

48:55.266 --> 48:57.200 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
It will just take a few minutes.

48:57.200 --> 48:58.566 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And you have my phone number.

48:58.566 --> 49:01.200 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
You can call me for anything.

49:01.200 --> 49:04.633 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: A few
minutes later, accompanied
by her husband, they
were on the way to Dr.

49:05.366 --> 49:06.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
