49:08.800 --> 49:11.233 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
WOMAN (through translator):
I was afraid at first.

49:11.233 --> 49:13.233 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
WOMAN (through translator):
But, today, no problems, right?

49:13.233 --> 49:16.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WOMAN (through translator):
No problem today, but I
