49:16.233 --> 49:20.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: The hope is
that she will help spread the
word and a culture of preventive

49:20.800 --> 49:22.233 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
care, says Dr. Uma Singh.

49:22.233 --> 49:24.300 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
DR.

49:24.300 --> 49:28.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
UMA SINGH: So, it is
like motivating them to
go for the checkup for
prevention of cancer,

49:29.700 --> 49:33.433 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
