49:34.933 --> 49:37.666 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
Then you have to ensure
that there have to
be good facilities.

49:37.666 --> 49:41.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: That much
larger job of building a better
public health system will

49:41.800 --> 49:46.800 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
