its screening program
is set to scale up.

49:48.833 --> 49:51.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The state government has begun
to train workers to offer it in
all public health clinics based

49:53.333 --> 49:56.366 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
